look at application logs, debugger output, or stack traces instead, then check what files are available in the working directory.","outputTokens":507},"id":"6069a92a-86ef-45c9-971d-4b9186d8735e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:17:41.310Z","parentId":"3d6d39e1-bef9-432a-bccb-d36b8fb610c5"}
